      NETLIFY FORMS VERSION (uncomment if migrating to Netlify):

      <form
        name="registration"
        method="POST"
        data-netlify="true"
        class="space-y-6"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="registration" />
        <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="הרשמה חדשה לתערוכת סורגות" />

